00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:05.333
Amera was created on 7  october of 2002, 
becoming the first non-europe server, 
it was located in USA.

00:00:05.333 --> 00:00:08.333
On this new world, refugees from Antica
and Nova had seen an opportunity to restart
their lives and perhaps become an icon of Camera.

00:00:08.333 --> 00:00:13.333
