to take Amera over

00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:23.333
In one side were the refugees members of
a famous Antica's guild: Hokuten.

00:00:23.333 --> 00:00:28.333
At the other side were the Amera's
peasants, they had to gathering themselves
against the power abuse guild Boondock Saints (Hokuten)

00:00:28.333 --> 00:00:33.333
